    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the Medical Health Center, where health meets technology for a brighter, healthier future.</p>
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>We envision a world where access to healthcare information is a fundamental right. Our journey began with a simple yet powerful idea: to empower individuals with the knowledge and tools they need to take control of their health.</p>
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>We are a team of healthcare professionals, data scientists, and technology enthusiasts committed to making healthcare accessible and personalized. Our expertise in healthcare and technology has led to the creation of this platform, reflecting our commitment to your well-being.</p>
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>Our mission is to provide a seamless platform leveraging AI and machine learning to assist in health concerns and offer educational resources to enhance health literacy.</p>
        <h2>How We Do It</h2>
        <p>We use a robust machine learning model trained on a vast dataset of symptoms and diseases to generate accurate predictions, aiding you in making informed health decisions.</p>
        <h2>Your Well-being, Our Priority</h2>
        <p>Your health is our top priority. We aim to provide accurate predictions along with comprehensive disease information, including descriptions, precautions, medications, dietary advice, and workout tips.</p>
        <h2>Join Us on this Journey</h2>
        <p>Explore our platform, engage with educational content, and take control of your health journey. We are here to empower you with knowledge and support for a healthier future.</p>
